Class AnsiSqlDataTypeFactory

java.lang.Object
au.csiro.pathling.views.ansi.AnsiSqlDataTypeFactory
public class AnsiSqlDataTypeFactory extends Object
Factory class for creating Spark SQL DataTypes from ANSI SQL type definitions.
